{"timestamp": "2026-04-27T15:26:30.646295+00:00", "event_type": "chat.message", "run_id": "run_97db", "trace_id": "e89430c749d09ed0ba551b31a1d2a9a7", "span_id": "3f2fddb4c20656e6", "parent_span_id": null, "actor": {"agent_id": "agent_c0807ff1", "role": "assistant", "agent_name": "Root Agent"}, "payload": {"message_id": 4, "content": "Tamam — siteye girdim ve sayfayı açtım.\n\n- Yüklendiği URL: https://scaa.us/article.php?id=2\n- Sayfa başlığı: \"Shelby County Aviation Association\"\n- Görüntüde görülenler: üstte SCAA logosu, üst menüde \"Dues Renewal | Member Login\" linkleri; sol tarafta menü: Home, About Us, Programs, Airport Info, Calendar, Join Now!, Contact Us. Orta bölümde başlık \"About the Shelby County Aviation Association\" ve aşağıdaki başlangıç paragrafı görünüyor:\n\n  \"Founded in 2005, The Shelby County Aviation Association was created to promote what our members believe is one of the most important infrastructure components in Shelby County, Alabama - The Shelby County Airport. The SCAA believes this mile of runway and supporting facilities provide an essential ingredient in the successful economic development of Shelby County while making an important contribution to the quality of life of Shelby County residents.\"\n\nNe yapmak istersin? Örneğin:\n- Anasayfaya veya başka bir menüye gitmemi ister misin (Programs, Contact Us, vs.)?\n- \"Member Login\" ya da \"Dues Renewal\" linklerine tıklayayım mı?\n- Sayfadaki metni tamamen çıkarıp özetleyeyim veya kaydedeyim?\n\nYönlendir, ben hallederim.", "metadata": {}}, "status": "logged", "error": null, "source": "sondra.chat"}
